{"tid":1261884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七一升旗禮 將不安排學生及制服團體出席","createTime":"2019-06-27T12:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T12:30:26.000Z","uid":80516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"51e146bdfea9c9655255733978e667aca63ff672","tid":1261884,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"2019年6月27日 上午9:01<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署回覆，因應近日社會情況及基於安全考慮，七一升旗禮，將不會安排學生及制服團體出席。<br />\n<br />\n多個制服團隊日前陸續接獲當局通知，不用參與下周一的回歸22周年升旗禮。<br />\n<br />\n醫療輔助隊回覆本台查詢時表示，在星期二下午接獲民政事務總署的通知，指升旗典禮的安排有所改變，醫療輔助隊不用參與。<br />\n<br />\n有人在網上號召，呼籲在6月30日金紫荊廣場集合，留守到七一當日，期間派發歌詞，教人唱聖詩，阻礙升旗禮進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465357-20190627.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465357-20190627.htm&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=1d663466\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465357-20190627.htm&h=b8228b2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465357-20190627.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7a6f845ce7b052f6eecda1f83fa63f31e4cf5e96","tid":1261884,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"共賊圍內升旗打飛機 粉飾太平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}